data.description: Nestled on a generous 0.48 acre lot, this captivating 3 bedroom, 2 bath home offers the perfect blend of convenience and serenity. Boasting easy access to interstate and close proximity to all amenities, this hidden gem is truly a rare find. Step inside and be greeted by an inviting kitchen that will leave culinary enthusiasts in awe. Equipped with a gas cooktop, this gourmet haven promise endless possibilities for creating delectable masterpieces. As you explore further, your eyes will be drawn to the mesmerizing gas log fireplace adorned with an expansive hearth - an idyllic spot for gathering around during cozy winter evenings. Outside, discover a backyard oasis enclosed by a sturdy chain-link fence. Complete with a storage building and carport featuring convenient electric wiring, there's ample space to store outdoor toys or embark on exciting DIY projects. And let's not forget the incredible addition of the Generac generator installed to ensure peace of mind even during power outages. Situated on a peaceful dead-end street lined with majestic trees, this enchanting home offers tranquility at its finest. Don't miss your chance to call this extraordinary retreat yours. Schedule your private tour today!
